OL,3,CPolice release 'shocking' footage of
OL,4,Cdangerous driving at car meet
OL,6,FPolice have released "shocking" video
OL,7,Ffootage of a driver "dangerously"
OL,8,Fdrifting around a roundabout at an
OL,9,Fillegal car meet, putting watching
OL,10,Fcrowds at "risk of being seriously
OL,11,Finjured".
OL,13,FDaniel Broomfield, 23, of Ticonderoga
OL,14,FGardens, Southampton, was sentenced at
OL,15,FWinchester Crown Court on 25 September
OL,16,Fto a 27-week prison sentence suspended
OL,17,Ffor 12 months, having previously
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to dangerous driving.
