OL,6,FHe was also banned from driving for 12
OL,7,Fmonths and ordered to carry out unpaid
OL,8,Fwork and a rehabilitation programme.
OL,10,FA Hampshire Constabulary spokesman
OL,11,Fsaid that the footage was taken at a
OL,12,Fcar meet in Portfield Road, Portsmouth
OL,13,Fon 28 December 2024, and showed
OL,14,FBroomfield driving the pink BMW shown
OL,15,Fin the video.
