OL,3,CPolice release 'shocking' footage of
OL,4,Cdangerous driving at car meet
OL,6,FThe force spokesman said: "This
OL,7,Ffootage shows the shocking moment a
OL,8,Fdangerous driver drifted around a
OL,9,Froundabout at an illegal car meet in
OL,10,FPortsmouth, while crowds watched on
OL,11,Fdespite the risk of being seriously
OL,12,Finjured."
OL,14,FHe added: "More than 200 offences
OL,15,Finvolving illegal car meets in
OL,16,FHampshire have been dealt with in just
OL,17,Fover a year, as part of our efforts to
OL,18,Fstamp out the blight of dangerous and
OL,19,Fanti-social driving on our roads.
