OL,6,F"Our robust response to these
OL,7,Fincidents, which cause misery for
OL,8,Flocal residents as well as posing a
OL,9,Fgreat risk to innocent motorists, has
OL,10,Fled to 215 offences being dealt with
OL,11,Fsince August 2025.
OL,13,F"As a result, more than #13,000 in
OL,14,Ffines and 69 penalty points have been
OL,15,Fhanded out to offenders, four people
OL,16,Fhave been disqualified and 76 Fixed
OL,17,FPenalty Notices have been issued.
OL,19,F"In the most serious of cases, we have
OL,20,Fbrought 54 prosecutions to court."
