OL,6,FSgt James Hall said: "Residents,
OL,7,Fmotorists and our roads policing teams
OL,8,Fhave had enough with these groups of
OL,9,Fdrivers selfishly taking over public
OL,10,Froads and car parks and we will not
OL,11,Ftolerate it in Hampshire and the Isle
OL,12,Fof Wight.
OL,14,F"We will continue to prosecute these
OL,15,Fdrivers and I hope these recent cases
OL,16,Fserve as a warning ` you won't get
OL,17,Faway with it."
